---
title: Double Salmon & Sunny Veggie Toss with Balsamic Glaze
description: Salmon is always nice cooked with light flavours, but a dark and rich balsamic glaze really takes it up a notch. With delicious root veggies in a cosy and vibrant toss, this might be the new best way to eat salmon.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b831d787e74f1041b20d07-c81d4edc.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/67b831d787e74f1041b20d07-en-NZ.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/double-mediterranean-salmon-and-winter-veggie-toss-67b831d787e74f1041b20d07
servings: 2
